      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "The big-money network of oil tycoon Charles Koch has been particularly active in trying to keep its political operations completely obscure. At the federal level, the Koch network has "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            18
          ],
          1,
          "been waging calculated warfare"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " against both the DISCLOSE Act and the For The People Act. Lobbying disclosures reveal that Koch Industries’ lobbying arm hired the corporate law firm Akin, Gump, Strauss, Hauer & Feld to lobby on the bill in the "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            19
          ],
          1,
          "second"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          ", "
        ],
